1. no change sending 250 mac per second and 54k macs and an age out of 2 mins.
at the end of one minute we have learnt 250x60 macs = 15000, 15k macs per minutes.
1 min - 15k S - 15k L
2 min - 30k S - 30K L
3 min - 45K S - 30K L
4 min - 60K S - 30K L

15 - 30 - 32.7K (45K)

Collect top and pmap memory before problem and after problem, collect pmap after every 1 mins.
l2 show
show resource:
root@localhost#
root@localhost#
